# Layout and Design

- Mobile-first: base at 375px, then sm/md/lg/xl breakpoints
- **Flexbox only** for page and section layout — never CSS Grid or absolute layout without explicit user permission
- Dashboard shell: max-width 1440px, 20px horizontal margins
- Tailwind - stick to Tailwind throughout, don't mix and match styling
- Semantic HTML, logical heading order, keyboard focus on interactive widgets
- Border radius: 10px (`--radius-md`) on cards, buttons, inputs, tags
- Depth: inset box-shadows on recessed surfaces; same-hue gradients only
- Icons via PrimeIcons/SVG — not Unicode emoji
- Prefer consistent variables over hardcoded values

# Font

- **Sansation** — all UI text except section card titles
- **PT Serif** — `h2` section titles only (semibold via global base rule)

# Font Weights

Use standard Tailwind utilities — defaults are not overridden:

| Utility | Weight |
|---------|--------|
| `font-normal` | 400 |
| `font-medium` | 500 |
| `font-semibold` | 600 |
| `font-bold` | 700 |

Global `h1`–`h4` use `font-semibold` (600); `strong`/`b` use `font-bold` (700). Tagline weight is `--font-accent-weight` on `.text-accent`.
